This paper is about question answering over knowledge bases (KB-QA) using neural models, which falls under the intersection of natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also involves deep learning techniques (cs.LG) and deals with knowledge bases (cs.DB).
